Package com.prms.entity

Class Appointment

java.lang.Object
com.prms.entity.Appointment
@Entity public class Appointment extends Object
The Appointment class represents an appointment made by a patient with a doctor. It contains fields for the appointment date, patient's email, phone number, diseases, doctor ID, patient's address, status of the appointment, and medical description.
Since:
05/05/2023
Version:

Author:
